high_descs: Walk out of the bedroom, into the hallway, make a right then continue into the kitchen over to the kitchen countertop with the microwave.
Pick up the potato from the kitchen counter next to the microwave.
Walk slightly to the left to the microwave on the kitchen counter.
Open the microwave door, place the potato inside, close the door and heat, remove the potato and close the door.
Turn to the right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the double fridge doors, place the potato on the left side of the second shelf from the bottom and close the fridge doors.
anns.task_desc: Place the microwaved potato into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight to reach the countertop.

Put the potato in to the microwave.
Then take the potato turn right to reach the fridge.
Put the potato into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Pick the potato from the microwave and put the potato into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the countertop on your left.
Pick up the potato from the table.
Put the potato in the microwave oven.
